AI Email Outreach Agent

An automated, end-to-end AI agent that scrapes websites, summarizes company information, generates personalized cold emails using LLMs, and sends them with human-like delays â€” all fully hands-free.

Built with Groq, Python, BeautifulSoup, and SMTP, this system is a practical example of applied AI engineering and automation.

ğŸš€ Features
âœ“ Fully automated outreach pipeline

For each lead, the agent:

Reads lead data from CSV

Scrapes the company's website

Summarizes what the company does using an LLM

Generates a personalized cold email (JSON-formatted)

Sends the email via SMTP

Logs the result with timestamps

Waits a random delay (mimics human behavior)

âœ“ AI-powered personalization

Uses LLMs (Groq API) to:

Extract meaningful website information

Condense it into a short business summary

Generate a high-quality, multi-paragraph, non-templated email

Enforce strict constraints (formatting, wording, JSON structure)

No two emails are the same.

âœ“ Human-like behavior

To prevent spam-like patterns:

Randomized delays

Unique wording

Varied sentence structure

Personalized references based on website summary

âœ“ Modular architecture

The project is fully modularized:

