âš™ï¸ How It Works (Flow)

Load Leads
Reads leads.csv â†’ extracts name, email, company, website.

Scrape Website
Downloads HTML â†’ extracts title, meta description, H1 â†’ cleans + truncates.

Summarize Website (LLM)
Converts raw website text into a 1â€“2 sentence description.

Generate Email (LLM)
Strictly enforced:

100â€“120 words

2â€“3 paragraphs

Personalization

Exactly one mention of 3D visuals

No use of â€œFrom â€ (to avoid Gmail quote formatting)

JSON output only

Send Email via SMTP
Fully automated.

Log Result
Saves:

timestamp

lead info

subject

email body

send status

Random Delay
Waits a human-like number of seconds before the next lead.

ğŸ“ CSV Format

Your leads.csv should include:

Name,Company,Email,Website
John Doe,Acme Inc,john@acme.com,https://acme.com
...


Invalid rows are skipped automatically.

ğŸ”§ Setup
1. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Add your .env
GROQ_API_KEY=your_key
EMAIL_ADDRESS=hello@yourdomain.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your_smtp_app_password

3. Run the agent
python main.py

